Global Coagulant Market Insights
Coagulant Market size was valued at USD 7.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 10.8 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 5.1% from 2024 to 2030.

Coagulant Market Overview
The coagulant market is projected to grow at a substantial pace, driven by increasing demand across various industries, including water treatment, paper production, and textiles. In 2024, the global coagulant market was valued at approximately USD 3.5 billion and is expected to reach USD 5.5 billion by 2030, with a CAGR of 7.5% during the forecast period. The growing concerns regarding water scarcity and pollution are encouraging investment in water treatment solutions, particularly in emerging economies. Additionally, coagulants play a crucial role in food and beverage processing, which further boosts market growth.

